productDes: This easy-to-read display measures temperature and humidity while recording maximum values. Features include a 12/24-hour clock, alarm with snooze, and a temperature trend indicator. It also displays the time, date, month, and week. Designed for versatility, it can stand on a table or be mounted on a wall.

Stay organized with this multifunctional pen holder set, featuring a built-in digital alarm clock. Perfect for storing pens, scissors, and notes, it supports a 12/24-hour display, alarm, snooze, and countdown functions. Powered by 2 AAA batteries, it adds both functionality and elegance to any desk, whether at home or in the office.

This modern electronic alarm clock doubles as a phone charger, ensuring efficient charging via USB power. It features voice control, adjustable brightness, and supports up to three alarms for added convenience. Compatible with various charging devices, it operates via USB or 4 AAA batteries.

This digital alarm clock features a 4.5-inch LCD display that shows the time (12/24 hours), temperature (째C/째F), and calendar with separate buttons for easy access. Made from durable ABS material, it is safe for kids.

This elegant multifunctional pen holder features a digital LCD alarm clock and countdown timer, displaying time, date, day, month, and temperature. It accommodates pens, pencils, and markers, has push-button pop-out drawers for storage, and includes a battery. Size: 8.5 cm x 11 cm, color: black.

This digital clock features a large LCD display for easy reading and portability. It monitors indoor temperature and humidity, promoting health benefits. It can be placed on a desk or hung on a wall, powered by an included AAA battery. Includes alarm and calendar functions.

This multifunctional weather monitor provides a 12 to 24-hour forecast with conditions like sunny, cloudy, and rain. It displays temperature (째F/째C), humidity, highs/lows, calendar, time, and alarm on a large LCD screen. Powered by two AAA batteries.

This multifunction digital clock features a mirror design with a large display for time, alarm, snooze, temperature, and night mode. It has adjustable brightness, USB or battery power options, and gentle alarm sounds, making it a perfect gift and an elegant bedroom accessory.

This 7-color changing digital LED alarm clock displays time, date, week, and temperature. Easy-to-use buttons allow for customization. Lightweight and perfect for travel, it's an ideal gift for kids or corporate branding. Operates on 3 AAA batteries or an AC adapter.

Beautiful clock with sharp edges, showing humidity and temperature with weather icons (sunny, cloudy, rainy). Records min/max/current humidity and temperature. Displays temperature in Celsius or Fahrenheit. Offers two display options: LCD with backlight or see-through.
